    "http://schema.org/url": [
      {
        "@id": "https://ww3.ticketpro.ca/event.php?event_id=10778"
      }
    ],
    "http://schema.org/name": [
      {
        "@value": "BABES, BABES, BABES! Burlesque and Drag Show"
      }
    ],
    "http://schema.org/description": [
      {
        "@value": "\n<p>4 beautiful BABES tease, titillate and bring you the babe-liest Burlesque and Drag show around!</p>\n\n<p>The  <b>BABES, BABES, BABES!</b> show is a jam-packed, laugh out loud, adults only cabaret! The show combines burlesque, drag, comedy, extravagant costumes, showstopping group numbers and naughty humour in a raucous spectacle that will leave you wanting more! Featuring an award winning cast of cabaret artists, each at the top of their field, the BABES show is the perfect way to spice up your night! </p>\n\n<p>In addition to all the sultry teases, the naughty jokes, and the sparkly thongs, the Babes celebrate sexuality, LGBTQ identities, and body confidence with inspiring performances and heartfelt moments.</p>\n\n<p>Perfect for a date night, a celebration or a girl's night out. So grab a ticket, grab a beverage and indulge in this special adults only evening of cabaret entertainment!</p>\n\n<p><b>FEATURING:</b><br>\n<i>World's #1 Babe: BonBon Bombay<br>\nRuthless Babe: Wrong Note Rusty<br>\nWhatta Babe: Selena Vyle<br>\nAnd The Babe Himself: James & The Giant Pasty</i></p>\n\n<p><b>Praise for the Babes, Babes, Babes Burlesque and Drag Tour from audience members:</b></p>\n\n<p><i>'FANTASTIC AMAZING HILARIOUS BEAUTIFUL ENTERTAINMENT!!! Come back to the island again!! And to a bigger venue! There was so many others that wanted to come, but it was sold out! ❤ You all were wonderful! Good luck on the rest of your tour!'</i><br>\nJess B. - Charlottetown, PEI</p>\n\n<p><i>'Saw you in Owen Sound! Went as a spur of the moment with a friend who had an extra ticket 🎫 Didn't know what to expect, could not stop laughing, and clapping what a fantastic show ! I hope you come back to Owen Sound, my Mom now wants to see you guys! ♥ ♥'</i><br>\nMegan J. - Owen Sound, ON</p>\n\n<p><i>'An unforgettable night of body positive performances, creativity and pure talent. The Babes always bring the fun'</i><br>\nErin S - Stratford, ON</p>\n\n<p><i>'Sextacular! Made me laugh, made me wet, and made me alive with joy through their incredible art 😍'</i><br>\nLuna M. - Toronto, ON</p>\n\n<p><i>'Just saw you guys at the Imperial and it was FANTASTIC!! My mom and I were in the splash zone and she made a joke to 'Keep it clean for her little boy' who is 26 😂 Made for a good gag 😂 Really hope you all come back!! ♥'</i><br>\nPJ - Saint John, NB</p>\n\n<p><i>'After several years of seeing the BABES, I'm already waiting with bated breath for BABES 2026!'</i><br>\nSpoilers Photography - Halifax, NS</p>\n\n<p><b>19+</b></p>\n\n<style>\n.location-page-temp {display: block!important;}\n</style>\n\n"
      }
    ],
