      }
    ],
    "http://schema.org/name": [
      {
        "@value": "Ben Caplan"
      }
    ],
    "http://schema.org/description": [
      {
        "@value": "<p>Ben Caplan is a singer, songwriter, and live performer known for his unmistakable baritone voice and emotionally immersive concerts. Blending folk, blues, gospel, and Eastern European influences, his music often feels less like a performance and more like a shared ritual—songs shaped by breath, silence, poetry, and raw emotion.</p>\n\n<p>Since releasing his latest album, The Flood, Caplan has been busy touring internationally with his band. Between those larger production shows, Caplan is making time for more intimate solo performances. Sharing brand new songs and old favourites, this will be a night to remember. Don't miss this rare chance to see Ben Caplan stripped back and up close here in Truro!\n </p>\n\n<style>\n@media screen and (max-width: 600px){iframe{width:100%;}}\n</style>"
      }
