    "http://schema.org/name": [
      {
        "@value": "Gypsy: Premiere Tribute To Fleetwood Mac"
      }
    ],
    "http://schema.org/description": [
      {
        "@value": "<p>GYPSY brings you the ultimate tribute to Fleetwood Mac, featuring accomplished musicians who deliver a world-class performance.</p> \n\n<p>Fleetwood Mac's iconic songs transcend generations, captivating music fans everywhere. Their award-winning album Rumours has sold nearly 50 million copies, and the band has achieved international acclaim with numerous Billboard-charting hits.</p> \n\n<p>The GYPSY Fleetwood Mac experience is a truly authentic tribute to the band, showcasing their greatest hits of all time. With powerful renditions of songs from their extensive catalogue—including Stevie Nicks' memorable duets with Don Henley and Tom Petty—this spectacular show is a must-see for Fleetwood Mac fans.</p> \n\n<p>Repertoire highlights include:</p> \n\n<p>Dreams<br>\nGo Your Own Way<br>\nRhiannon<br>\nDon't Stop<br>\nThe Chain<br>\n...and many more fan favourites!</p> \n\n\n<style>\n.location-page-temp {\n    display: block!important;\n}\n</style>"
      }
    ],
