    ],
    "http://schema.org/name": [
      {
        "@value": "Lady Soul"
      }
    ],
    "http://schema.org/description": [
      {
        "@value": "<p>Channeling soul and funk divas of yesterday and today, this nine-piece ensemble performs dynamic renditions of classic tracks by Aretha Franklin, Jackson 5, Christina Aguilera, Béyonce, and more.</p>\n\n<p>Featuring Kelley Mooney, Emi Smith, and Heather McIsaac on vocals, the group includes Mark Parsons and Joanna McKearney on horns, Dave Gordon on keys, Chad Deagle on guitar, Jason Rogerson on bass, and Kirk White on drums.</p>\n \n<p>Featuring special guest Donovan Morgan on guitar for this performance, expect a night of memorable songs that will have you dancing in your seat!</p>\n\n\n<p><b>If you would like to make a reservation to enjoy dinner before the show, please call the venue at: 902-964-2255 or email them at <a href='mailto:harmonyhousePEIresos@gmail.com'>harmonyhousePEIresos@gmail.com</a>!<br>Please note: On 2pm matinee days, The Lounge is open for dinner reservations 3:30pm onward, after the 2pm performance.<br><br>\nFor ticket details, visit Harmony House Theatre on-line at <a href='https://harmonyhousepei.com/' target='_blank'><u>harmonyhousepei.com</u></a> or call the box office at 1-888-311-9090.</i></b></p>\n\n<p><b>Harmony House Gift Certificates are not redeemable through Ticketpro. Please contact Harmony House directly to redeem.</b></p>\n\n<p><b><font size='+1'>TICKET PURCHASES ARE FINAL AND NON-REFUNDABLE</b></font></p>\n\n\n<style>\n.location-page-temp {\n    display: block!important;\n}\n</style>\n\n"
      }
    ],
