    "http://schema.org/url": [
      {
        "@id": "https://ww3.ticketpro.ca/event.php?event_id=10636"
      }
    ],
    "http://schema.org/name": [
      {
        "@value": "The Megastars of Country Music"
      }
    ],
    "http://schema.org/description": [
      {
        "@value": "<p>The MEGASTARS OF COUNTRY MUSIC is an exciting, fun-filled, live concert experience featuring tributes to country music's most legendary singers and songwriters. This incredible show which features Larry Turner and Doug Brewin pays homage to the incredible careers of ALAN JACKSON, GEORGE STRAIT and BROOKS & DUNN</p>\n\n <p>The MEGASTARS OF COUNTRY is a musical celebration saluting some of the greatest country hits ever recorded by some of the most famous and respected stars. What makes the show extraordinary is the performers using their own natural voices and appearance to sound and look exactly like the real artists in concert. Their mannerisms, vocals and authentic stage costumes cover every detail which captures the closest experience you'll ever get to the real deal!</p>\n \n<p>The show has appeared countless times to sold-out audiences, standing ovations and incredible reviews.</p>\n\n<iframe width='560' height='315' src='https://www.youtube.com/embed/4zTTTUuZbdM?si=OFEMFdHAgkbbnC1S' title='YouTube video player' frameborder='0' allow='accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share' referrerpolicy='strict-origin-when-cross-origin' allowfullscreen></iframe>\n\n<style>\n.location-page-temp {display: block!important;}\n@media screen and (max-width: 600px){iframe{width:100%;}}\n</style>"
      }
    ],
